{"tid":274662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【渾水預告】Carson Block明公布沽空香港上市公司","createTime":"2017-06-07T13:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T14:52:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74393aebddba3d4e5364d6f49e653f5046af77bc","tid":274662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170606/photo/bkn-20170606103055060-0606_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170607051521\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170606103055060-0606_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170607051521&h=311d0090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沽空機構渾水(Muddy Waters)創辦人Carson Block接受外電訪問時表示，香港若干公司存在欺詐，更揚言新的沽空目標將是香港上市的公司，有關詳情將於明日公布。<br />\n<br />\n今次已非Carson Block首次預告會狙擊港股。去年12月，他接受外國傳媒訪問時，亦揚言會繼續在香港上市公司發掘沽空目標，表示自己一直以來都喜歡沽空徹頭徹尾的「老千股」，港股市場正好具備，因此香港繼續是他搵食的地方。<br />\n<br />\n輝山乳業(06863)去年底被渾水狙擊，股價隨即暴跌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170606/bkn-20170606103055060-0606_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170606%2Fbkn-20170606103055060-0606_00842_001.html&d=Lwq37QuzZXg%2B2cZCUkfRWDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3d013cfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170606/bkn-20170606103055060-0606_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9216d3e189619ecccaad954f7a63e6b195c69942","tid":274662,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"樓主訓左兩日？"},{"pid":"ed532721249a09c5d161f680a127e899563a4e9d","tid":274662,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主訓左兩日？</blockquote><br />\n五毛洗版是常識吧？唔好推啦"},{"pid":"c1676312d078263b7048df4f12753f8f4cde59a5","tid":274662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主訓左兩日？</blockquote><br />\n五毛洗版是常識吧？唔好推啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔係五毛,唔好屈得就屈,sorry囉,出舊post"},{"pid":"8d77e3772ab0959667dabe51e7038785bc21d1c8","tid":274662,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"班友唔驚比人......."}]}